Network intrusion Prevention(NIPS) - 


Colleration Engine - to deal with the task


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

NIPS - type of detection methods included; Behavioral, signature-based, rule-based and Heuristic.

Port Mirroring and Network Taps are tools used with NIDs and NIPS.

NIDs is most often set up as out-of-band, NIPS is typically in-band.

